title: Strong Bad's Cool Game For Attractive People [Season 1]
description:
Strong Bad's Cool game for attractive people, season 1. Includes all the episodes from season 1. 
 
Info
=========================================================
Strong Bad's Cool Game for Attractive People (abbreviated SBCG4AP) is an episodic series of point-and-click adventure games developed by Telltale Games based on the Homestar Runner web cartoon and starring Strong Bad. The first episode, Homestar Ruiner, was released on August 11, 2008 for the Wii (as a WiiWare game) and Windows.
========================================================


Instructions:
Install the Demo's to wherever, then place the cracked exe in the folder the episode is in.

Cracks were made by pimpedtuber, Sharpevil, and Twisted EndZ.

Enjoy.
